These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, satire, action
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, house, folk
1. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
2. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the fan of classical is the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
5. the fan of house is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | drama | satire |
| Music-Genre    | house    | folk | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
City: hamburg, rome, prague
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dunhill, swisher
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City       | rome | prague | hamburg |
| Cigar   | swisher    | dunhill     | blend        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, grapes, kale
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, dutch, australian
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the dutch is on the left of the mexican##1
3. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Food         | kale     | grapes | artichoke |
| Nationality   | dutch | mexican     | australian  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, mechanic, accountant
City: rome, berlin, liverpool
1. the mechanic is the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the analyst is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the mechanic is in an even position##4
4. the mechanic is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Job   | accountant | mechanic  | analyst  |
| City         | rome  | berlin | liverpool |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, classical, trance
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, townhouse
1. the fan of trance is between the fan of house and the farmhouse house##2
2. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre         | house   | trance | classical    |
| House   | gothic-revival | townhouse     | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, salsa
There are 3 different nationalities: french, german, chinese
1. the fan of ambient is the german##1
2. the chinese is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | salsa | ambient   |
| Nationality   | chinese     | french    | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
3 different games are played: snooker, billiard, monopoly
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, handball, swimming
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing snooker is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person playing monopoly##2
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker | billiard |
| Sport           | handball         | water-polo         | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, scooter
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, water-polo, tennis
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person driving the motorbike##2
2. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Transport   | ship | scooter | motorbike |
| Sport    | water-polo    | biathlon | tennis     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There 3 different types of food: papaya, cauliflower, carrot
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, lilac, purple
1. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Food   | carrot   | cauliflower  | papaya  |
| Color         | purple | lilac | red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, pall-mall, davidoff
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, photography, chess
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Cigar   | alhambra    | davidoff      | pall-mall |
| Hobby       | photography | chess | skydiving   |

