.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, superhero, thriller
3 different pets are kept: rat, frog, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person watching family movies is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
4. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | superhero | family |
| Pet     | frog     | rat   | horse        |

