.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
City: edinburgh, liverpool, hamburg
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, tea
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person drinking water is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| City   | hamburg  | edinburgh | liverpool   |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | tea   | water |

