.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, dahlia
There 3 different types of food: radish, onion, zucchini
1. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growsiris and the person eating onion##2
2. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating onion is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Flower   | iris | dahlia | tulip |
| Food     | radish    | zucchini  | onion   |

