.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, may
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, japanese, thai
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the japanese is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | july  | may     | february |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian | thai    |

