.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, hamster
House: victorian, modern, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the hamster is the modern house##1
4. the victorian house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Pet         | hamster | cat   | rabbit |
| House   | modern   | victorian | ranch-style      |

