.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, snake, mouse
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, cabbage, asparagus
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
2. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Pet      | fish | snake | mouse |
| Food   | cabbage   | asparagus          | pineapple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, daffodil
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Flower     | balloon-flower  | daffodil   | amaryllis |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts | family       |

 